/// # Console Web Application Package
///
/// This package provides web-based console functionality for the Vorpal Blade framework,
/// implementing servlet-based HTTP request handling for administrative operations.
///
/// ## Key Classes
///
/// - [Logout] - HTTP servlet that handles user logout operations via GET requests
///
/// ## Overview
///
/// The package extends the standard Java Servlet API to provide console management
/// capabilities within the Vorpal Blade application framework. It focuses on session
/// management and user authentication workflows through web-based interfaces.
///
/// The servlet implementations in this package handle HTTP requests for administrative
/// console operations, providing the necessary endpoints for user session management
/// and authentication control.
///
/// @see javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
/// @see javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest
/// @see javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse
package org.vorpal.blade.applications.console.webapp;
